1
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:44,679
(In Between)

2
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:47,599
(Episode 13)

3
00:01:59,560 --> 00:02:00,560
Gao Peng.

4
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,799
I'm in front of your house.

5
00:02:01,879 --> 00:02:02,920
Where are you?

6
00:02:05,359 --> 00:02:08,439
(Little Peng: Enter the password to get inside. I'm in a meeting.)

7
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,530
What the heck?

8
00:02:23,120 --> 00:02:24,638
I'll drink.

9
00:02:24,639 --> 00:02:25,719
- Okay. - Okay.

10
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,479
Hello, Ms. He.

11
00:02:35,199 --> 00:02:36,280
I'm Emily.

12
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,599
This is Alex.

13
00:02:37,639 --> 00:02:39,096
He was Gao Peng's classmate when he studied abroad.

14
00:02:39,120 --> 00:02:40,120
He's also my cousin.

15
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:41,719
Hello.

16
00:02:42,599 --> 00:02:43,879
This is Kathy and Allen.

17
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,279
They were Gao Peng's classmates.

18
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,359
And Jack.

19
00:02:46,360 --> 00:02:47,438
Fiona.

20
00:02:47,439 --> 00:02:48,639
They're Gao Peng's colleagues.

21
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,800
Where is Gao Peng?

22
00:02:55,479 --> 00:02:57,360
Mr. Gao is in his study.

23
00:02:57,439 --> 00:02:58,520
He has an online meeting.

24
00:03:00,639 --> 00:03:01,960
We met in Jiangzhou before.

25
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,000
Do you remember?

26
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,839
Yes, I remember.

27
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,919
Of course I do.

28
00:03:09,719 --> 00:03:11,816
Anyway, we have to wait for Mr. Gao to finish his meeting.

29
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,200
Why don't I show you around first?

30
00:03:14,439 --> 00:03:16,000
Hello, Ms. He. I'm Gumina.

31
00:03:16,039 --> 00:03:17,039
Welcome to Hong Kong.

32
00:03:17,040 --> 00:03:18,120
Please change your shoes.

33
00:03:22,439 --> 00:03:23,800
- Thank you. - You're welcome.

34
00:03:31,319 --> 00:03:33,439
Everyone likes to visit Gao Peng's house.

35
00:03:34,319 --> 00:03:35,360
It's very convenient here.

36
00:03:42,400 --> 00:03:43,560
Look at this balcony.

37
00:03:43,599 --> 00:03:44,599
It's beautiful.

38
00:04:12,599 --> 00:04:13,960
Just as Su Su predicted,

39
00:04:15,120 --> 00:04:16,759
she must have a sense of crisis.

40
00:04:18,639 --> 00:04:20,279
Is this really a good idea?

41
00:04:22,519 --> 00:04:24,439
We'll find out whether it's a good idea or not.

42
00:04:24,730 --> 00:04:25,730
Don't be impatient.

43
00:04:27,000 --> 00:04:29,639
Sometimes, when we look at things from a different perspective,

44
00:04:30,610 --> 00:04:32,570
many answers turn out to be completely different.

45
00:04:33,319 --> 00:04:34,360
What do you mean?

46
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,559
Have you ever thought that the real issue...

47
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:38,050
between you and He Zhi Nan...

48
00:04:38,560 --> 00:04:40,480
is that she doesn't truly grasp your importance?

49
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,800
In love,

50
00:04:42,000 --> 00:04:43,280
we all need a sense of security.

51
00:04:43,480 --> 00:04:46,000
However, too much security can backfire.

52
00:04:46,240 --> 00:04:47,319
Sometimes,

53
00:04:48,079 --> 00:04:49,839
a sense of crisis and a sense of security...

54
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,730
are two sides of the same coin.

55
00:04:52,199 --> 00:04:54,026
I heard that you've been in a long-distance relationship...

56
00:04:54,050 --> 00:04:55,169
for seven years,

57
00:04:55,170 --> 00:04:56,239
but the time you've actually spent together...

58
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,080
is less than a few months I've known Gao Peng.

59
00:04:58,959 --> 00:05:00,639
Come on. I'll show you your room.

60
00:05:01,959 --> 00:05:03,680
The clothes and cosmetics inside...

61
00:05:04,279 --> 00:05:05,479
were all carefully selected for you,

62
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,560
piece by piece,

63
00:05:06,610 --> 00:05:07,610
during my shopping trips...

64
00:05:07,611 --> 00:05:08,851
around Hong Kong with Gao Peng.

65
00:05:11,610 --> 00:05:13,319
You have to let her know...

66
00:05:13,480 --> 00:05:15,000
that you're surrounded by choices...

67
00:05:15,439 --> 00:05:16,439
and...

68
00:05:16,879 --> 00:05:17,959
temptations.

69
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:20,759
My favourite part of the house is the master bedroom.

70
00:05:21,879 --> 00:05:22,920
Is it nice?

71
00:05:23,439 --> 00:05:24,519
Yes.

72
00:05:24,879 --> 00:05:26,879
A bathtub with a view of the mountains.

73
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,279
I'll try it out tonight.

74
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:34,480
You should try it.

75
00:05:35,199 --> 00:05:36,879
Last night, I even told Gao Peng...

76
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,560
that if two people used it together,

77
00:05:38,720 --> 00:05:39,840
it'd be incredibly relaxing.

78
00:05:40,399 --> 00:05:41,680
Are you two close?

79
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,519
Not really.

80
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:46,560
However, Gao Peng is really thoughtful...

81
00:05:46,600 --> 00:05:48,199
and generous.

82
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,318
We all like him very much.

83
00:05:49,319 --> 00:05:50,398
Gao Peng.

84
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:51,438
Gao Peng!

85
00:05:51,439 --> 00:05:52,439
Gao Peng.

86
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,240
Nan Nan.

87
00:06:01,720 --> 00:06:03,159
- Gao Peng. - All right.

88
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,279
I miss you so much.

89
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,639
Are you looking for Yi Peng?

90
00:06:14,759 --> 00:06:16,079
I know you. Su Su.

91
00:06:23,199 --> 00:06:24,959
Here. Let me introduce you.

92
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:26,639
This is Han Su.

93
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:29,119
She's the lawyer who will soon be working with our company.

94
00:06:31,839 --> 00:06:32,920
Hello.

95
00:06:33,959 --> 00:06:35,040
Hello.

96
00:06:37,439 --> 00:06:38,879
Mr. Gao always talks about you.

97
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:40,359
I finally get to meet you today.

98
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:44,199
You must be tired from the trip.

99
00:06:44,399 --> 00:06:47,039
Do you want to wash your face and change into comfortable clothes?

100
00:06:50,040 --> 00:06:51,439
Go ahead.

101
00:07:03,639 --> 00:07:04,639
Nan Nan.

102
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,720
What's wrong?

103
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,319
Did I look...

104
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:24,680
really bad just now?

105
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:29,240
No.

106
00:07:29,680 --> 00:07:31,560
This happens to everyone right after deplaning.

107
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:32,639
Don't think too much.

108
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,958
Did I embarrass you?

109
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:35,959
No.

110
00:07:43,800 --> 00:07:44,838
I'll wait for you downstairs.

111
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,920
Unpack first.

112
00:07:51,199 --> 00:07:52,439
Han Han, I've thought about it.

113
00:07:53,519 --> 00:07:54,560
Once I'm in Hong Kong,

114
00:07:55,199 --> 00:07:57,399
I'll tell Gao Peng everything,

115
00:07:58,759 --> 00:08:00,039
including my innermost thoughts.

116
00:08:00,519 --> 00:08:02,079
What if he can't accept it?

117
00:08:04,120 --> 00:08:05,319
If he can't accept it,

118
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,759
we can...

119
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,120
just be friends or even strangers.

120
00:08:09,680 --> 00:08:10,759
I'm okay with that.

121
00:08:13,800 --> 00:08:16,200
The more I think about it, the more I feel something is off.

122
00:08:18,240 --> 00:08:19,640
He must be doing this on purpose...

123
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,079
to intimidate me.

124
00:08:21,519 --> 00:08:23,039
This place feels like a spider's lair,

125
00:08:23,720 --> 00:08:25,880
filled with all sorts of tricksters coming in and out.

126
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,160
Did you see how Gao Peng...

127
00:08:27,639 --> 00:08:29,279
is being fawned over by those tricksters?

128
00:08:30,279 --> 00:08:31,319
It's infuriating.

129
00:08:32,679 --> 00:08:33,840
He has really changed.

130
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:36,480
Why would I confess anything about Qu Yi Peng at this time?

131
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,759
I'm not that foolish.

132
00:08:44,759 --> 00:08:45,840
She's quite ordinary.

133
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:48,480
I don't think she's a match for Gao Peng.

134
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:52,279
That means her strengths are hidden away.

135
00:08:54,090 --> 00:08:55,879
No wonder Qing Wen likes to rip fans.

136
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,159
It's quite stress-relieving.

137
00:08:57,559 --> 00:08:58,639
Stress-relieving?

138
00:08:58,799 --> 00:09:00,000
What stress do you have?

139
00:09:00,480 --> 00:09:02,559
Emily, you're not going to do it for real, are you?

140
00:09:06,799 --> 00:09:09,279
Some people have their strengths hidden away.

141
00:09:09,919 --> 00:09:11,840
This makes them more rare,

142
00:09:12,210 --> 00:09:14,159
more valuable,

143
00:09:14,639 --> 00:09:15,919
and more difficult to deal with.

144
00:09:17,210 --> 00:09:18,279
Han Su.

145
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:20,720
Any man I desire,

146
00:09:21,090 --> 00:09:22,279
I can always get.

147
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,840
- Bye. - Bye.

148
00:09:33,919 --> 00:09:35,038
You don't have to see us out. Bye.

149
00:09:35,039 --> 00:09:36,158
Okay. You forgot your bag.

150
00:09:36,159 --> 00:09:37,210
Thank you.

151
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,535
Go be with your girlfriend.

152
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:40,039
You guys haven't met for a long time.

153
00:09:41,360 --> 00:09:42,919
I really like your big bathtub.

154
00:09:46,120 --> 00:09:47,159
- Bye, Mr. Gao. - Bye.

155
00:09:47,600 --> 00:09:48,600
Bye.

156
00:09:51,090 --> 00:09:52,120
Bye.

157
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:05,210
Leave it there.

158
00:10:05,679 --> 00:10:06,960
Someone will clean it up later.

159
00:10:07,559 --> 00:10:08,840
It's the same if I do it.

160
00:10:09,600 --> 00:10:11,240
If you do the work of a maid,

161
00:10:11,519 --> 00:10:13,798
she'll think you look down on her and feel that she is unprofessional.

162
00:10:13,799 --> 00:10:14,840
Just leave it there.

163
00:10:18,679 --> 00:10:20,840
You have a meeting tonight, right?

164
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:23,999
Han Su sent me a ton of materials that I need to review.

165
00:10:24,120 --> 00:10:25,360
We have a meeting tomorrow too.

166
00:10:29,720 --> 00:10:31,080
You can do whatever you want here.

167
00:10:59,200 --> 00:11:00,480
This person is my ex-boyfriend.

168
00:11:01,279 --> 00:11:04,120
When I found out about her existence,

169
00:11:04,240 --> 00:11:05,960
we hadn't completely broken up.

170
00:11:07,320 --> 00:11:09,399
If she's honest with you,

171
00:11:09,919 --> 00:11:11,039
will you forgive her?

172
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:12,879
If she lies to you,

173
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,639
will you give up completely?

174
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:39,279
I...

175
00:11:40,919 --> 00:11:42,240
I want to talk to you.

176
00:11:42,320 --> 00:11:43,640
Let me finish reading this first.

177
00:11:44,519 --> 00:11:45,840
I think we've grown too distant.

178
00:11:47,080 --> 00:11:49,000
We haven't seen each other for such a long time.

179
00:11:50,799 --> 00:11:51,959
It's not that I don't want to spend time with you.

180
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:53,279
- I'm really busy. - Busy?

181
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:55,799
I know you're busy.

182
00:11:57,399 --> 00:11:58,480
I'll just say a few words.

183
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,799
I came to Hong Kong...

184
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:01,879
to tell you this in person.

185
00:12:03,679 --> 00:12:04,759
I'll leave after that.

186
00:12:18,440 --> 00:12:19,799
After breaking up with you,

187
00:12:20,559 --> 00:12:22,159
I met a guy.

188
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:25,320
He was nice to me.

189
00:12:25,720 --> 00:12:26,799
He cared about me.

190
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:30,480
I was really into him for a while...

191
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,080
or maybe...

192
00:12:34,600 --> 00:12:36,400
I was just into the feeling of being in love.

193
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,080
When we broke up last time,

194
00:12:42,759 --> 00:12:44,480
I thought you were just throwing a tantrum.

195
00:12:44,960 --> 00:12:46,440
After all, when I returned last time,

196
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,279
we were still so close.

197
00:12:49,879 --> 00:12:51,639
I thought we could reconcile.

198
00:12:52,759 --> 00:12:53,799
I'm confused too.

199
00:12:55,919 --> 00:12:56,960
I'm confused...

200
00:12:58,600 --> 00:13:00,096
I'm confused as to why I feel so at ease...

201
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,720
- whenever I see you? - Stop it.

202
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:03,678
Since you chose him,

203
00:13:03,679 --> 00:13:05,239
as long as you're happy, that's enough.

204
00:13:06,519 --> 00:13:07,639
We broke up.

205
00:13:10,879 --> 00:13:12,519
I was really confused during that period.

206
00:13:13,799 --> 00:13:15,759
It felt like two selves were living inside me.

207
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,200
One said...

208
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:20,720
to keep it a secret from Gao Peng.

209
00:13:21,759 --> 00:13:23,320
He would be sad if he found out.

210
00:13:25,120 --> 00:13:26,360
The other insisted that...

211
00:13:27,679 --> 00:13:29,200
I can't betray the one I love.

212
00:13:32,759 --> 00:13:34,279
From the time I was 18...

213
00:13:34,840 --> 00:13:35,879
until now,

214
00:13:37,200 --> 00:13:39,759
you've always been the most important person to me.

215
00:13:41,519 --> 00:13:42,960
People can fool others,

216
00:13:44,440 --> 00:13:46,039
but how can one fool themselves?

217
00:13:50,000 --> 00:13:51,239
I felt so touched...

218
00:13:51,240 --> 00:13:52,416
when you came to my house last time...

219
00:13:52,440 --> 00:13:53,480
and gave me the bracelet.

220
00:13:56,360 --> 00:13:57,360
At that time,

221
00:13:57,840 --> 00:13:59,600
that guy was also pursuing me.

222
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:05,279
To be honest, I quite enjoyed...

223
00:14:05,360 --> 00:14:07,480
the excitement of such a dramatic situation.

224
00:14:10,200 --> 00:14:12,120
Perhaps it's a girl's vanity.

225
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:16,160
When I came to Hong Kong, I was really afraid.

226
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,279
I was afraid of making you sad,

227
00:14:25,799 --> 00:14:26,879
afraid of making you angry,

228
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:29,000
and also...

229
00:14:29,600 --> 00:14:30,639
afraid of losing you.

230
00:14:33,559 --> 00:14:35,240
However, after I came here, I realized...

231
00:14:36,559 --> 00:14:38,559
that you're no longer the Gao Peng I used to know.

232
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,399
I don't seem that important anymore.

233
00:14:44,240 --> 00:14:45,480
I can feel it.

234
00:14:48,240 --> 00:14:49,279
You love her very much.

235
00:14:49,399 --> 00:14:50,559
Perhaps she's...

236
00:14:54,320 --> 00:14:55,520
struggling internally as well.

237
00:15:01,600 --> 00:15:02,840
I've said what I wanted to say.

238
00:15:05,639 --> 00:15:06,639
I'm going back tomorrow.

239
00:15:08,519 --> 00:15:09,600
Nan Nan.

240
00:15:20,799 --> 00:15:23,120
You're the person I love the most in this world,

241
00:15:23,960 --> 00:15:25,440
even if you're confused for a moment.

242
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:30,600
You've been saying so much.

243
00:15:31,679 --> 00:15:33,080
So just tell me...

244
00:15:33,320 --> 00:15:34,639
if you love me at this moment.

245
00:15:37,799 --> 00:15:38,839
All right.

246
00:15:38,840 --> 00:15:40,120
Tell me that you love me.

247
00:15:44,200 --> 00:15:45,360
I love you.

248
00:15:49,600 --> 00:15:50,600
All right.

249
00:15:50,759 --> 00:15:51,759
I love you too.

250
00:15:57,240 --> 00:15:58,399
I love you.

251
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:11,960
(Baibaotang, Chinese herbal jelly)

252
00:16:14,559 --> 00:16:16,000
(Baibaotang)

253
00:16:17,559 --> 00:16:18,839
We've eaten too much spicy food.

254
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:20,558
How about having some herbal tea to reduce the heat?

255
00:16:20,559 --> 00:16:21,639
Sure.

256
00:16:26,679 --> 00:16:27,759
Here you go.

257
00:16:27,879 --> 00:16:29,120
What would you like?

258
00:16:29,879 --> 00:16:31,158
Two bowls of herbal tea.

259
00:16:31,159 --> 00:16:32,159
- Okay. - Thank you.

260
00:16:32,160 --> 00:16:33,240
Have a seat.

261
00:16:39,240 --> 00:16:40,279
Emily.

262
00:16:41,000 --> 00:16:42,039
Last time,

263
00:16:42,879 --> 00:16:44,199
you left your phone at Gao Peng's house.

264
00:16:44,200 --> 00:16:45,560
You did it on purpose, didn't you?

265
00:16:46,200 --> 00:16:47,279
Han Su.

266
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:48,879
Don't say it out loud.

267
00:16:51,279 --> 00:16:52,360
Be honest with me.

268
00:16:52,600 --> 00:16:54,399
How far have you and Gao Peng progressed?

269
00:16:55,399 --> 00:16:56,759
I remember Gao Peng said...

270
00:16:57,200 --> 00:16:58,519
he loves Northern food,

271
00:16:59,000 --> 00:17:00,239
so I purposely packed...

272
00:17:00,240 --> 00:17:01,680
a serving of grilled lamb kidneys...

273
00:17:01,759 --> 00:17:03,119
and delivered it to him last time.

274
00:17:03,559 --> 00:17:04,650
He was quite touched.

275
00:17:05,319 --> 00:17:06,479
He asked me if I was thirsty.

276
00:17:06,599 --> 00:17:07,680
Of course, I said I was.

277
00:17:07,960 --> 00:17:10,279
I asked him to open a bottle of Lafite for me.

278
00:17:11,680 --> 00:17:12,759
And then?

279
00:17:14,410 --> 00:17:17,279
Then he forgot that his bathtub was filling up...

280
00:17:17,480 --> 00:17:18,960
and it almost overflowed.

281
00:17:19,759 --> 00:17:23,359
I also took a moment to admire his master bedroom's large bathtub.

