00:33:53,039 --> 00:33:54,599
If you don't want to get back together,

563
00:33:54,759 --> 00:33:55,839
I can understand that.

564
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,680
I'm not a little girl anymore...

565
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:00,800
and you don't need to explain anything to me.

566
00:34:01,359 --> 00:34:02,440
I know...

567
00:34:03,039 --> 00:34:04,359
what happened between us.

568
00:34:04,759 --> 00:34:06,359
It's just that I realized it too late.

569
00:34:06,960 --> 00:34:07,960
Otherwise,

570
00:34:08,199 --> 00:34:09,679
I wouldn't have been so foolish...

571
00:34:09,769 --> 00:34:10,769
as to divorce you.

572
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,440
Don't think too much.

573
00:34:13,960 --> 00:34:15,329
It's not what you think.

574
00:34:16,239 --> 00:34:17,329
Then tell me.

575
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,000
What happened?

576
00:34:19,599 --> 00:34:22,039
I've explained everything to you about how things are.

577
00:34:22,719 --> 00:34:24,135
It's just that you don't believe me.

578
00:34:24,159 --> 00:34:25,599
There's nothing I can do about that.

579
00:34:28,519 --> 00:34:29,519
We can be frank...

580
00:34:30,199 --> 00:34:31,639
with each other.

581
00:34:32,639 --> 00:34:34,039
You can tell me the truth.

582
00:34:34,719 --> 00:34:36,239
I'm really calm right now.

583
00:34:38,119 --> 00:34:40,329
I admit I was wrong,

584
00:34:43,119 --> 00:34:44,808
so I can understand and accept it...

585
00:34:44,809 --> 00:34:46,329
if you yell at me or want me to leave.

586
00:34:47,769 --> 00:34:49,000
That's because deep down,

587
00:34:50,159 --> 00:34:52,559
this will always be my home.

588
00:34:53,039 --> 00:34:54,039
Does that mean...

589
00:34:54,599 --> 00:34:55,639
you still see us...

590
00:34:56,480 --> 00:34:57,768
as husband and wife in your heart?

591
00:34:57,769 --> 00:34:58,840
Of course.

592
00:35:03,719 --> 00:35:05,199
When we got divorced,

593
00:35:05,239 --> 00:35:07,079
all the assets were under my name.

594
00:35:08,119 --> 00:35:09,679
There's also my shares in your company.

595
00:35:10,769 --> 00:35:12,329
If we don't get back together,

596
00:35:13,039 --> 00:35:14,440
your losses will be substantial.

597
00:35:18,329 --> 00:35:19,489
The money is in your hands...

598
00:35:20,239 --> 00:35:21,519
and I'm here with you.

599
00:35:23,329 --> 00:35:24,920
I'm truly devoted to you.

600
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,079
I promise you.

601
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:33,559
From now on, I'll live well with you.

602
00:35:36,159 --> 00:35:37,639
What else do you have to worry about?

603
00:35:42,840 --> 00:35:44,719
Do you want the empire or the beauty?

604
00:35:46,000 --> 00:35:47,559
Think carefully.

605
00:35:49,679 --> 00:35:51,079
You don't have to decide now.

606
00:35:52,199 --> 00:35:53,479
Take your time to think it over.

607
00:35:55,079 --> 00:35:56,159
Both of us...

608
00:35:56,809 --> 00:35:58,129
have to think about it carefully.

609
00:36:13,159 --> 00:36:14,239
Su Su,

610
00:36:14,559 --> 00:36:17,119
I was packing for a business trip to Shanghai.

611
00:36:17,559 --> 00:36:18,679
Why were you looking for me?

612
00:36:19,289 --> 00:36:20,439
You didn't answer my calls.

613
00:36:20,440 --> 00:36:21,920
I was so worried about you.

614
00:36:22,400 --> 00:36:24,440
Why are you going to Shanghai at this time?

615
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:27,000
Aren't you just giving Zhou Bin a chance to find that woman?

616
00:36:27,329 --> 00:36:29,416
If I don't give him a chance, will he just sit around?

617
00:36:29,440 --> 00:36:30,519
Besides,

618
00:36:30,639 --> 00:36:32,839
what's the difference between once and countless times?

619
00:36:32,960 --> 00:36:34,400
Am I supposed to drop everything...

620
00:36:34,440 --> 00:36:35,575
and keep him tied to me every single day?

621
00:36:35,599 --> 00:36:37,559
I don't quite understand your strategy here.

622
00:36:37,679 --> 00:36:39,559
Didn't you say you want to win Zhou Bin back...

623
00:36:40,289 --> 00:36:42,039
and declare war on that woman?

624
00:36:43,039 --> 00:36:44,079
I hinted to Zhou Bin...

625
00:36:44,559 --> 00:36:45,695
that even if we get back together,

626
00:36:45,719 --> 00:36:47,305
I'd turn a blind eye to their relationship.

627
00:36:47,329 --> 00:36:48,639
That's what he wanted me to do.

628
00:36:49,329 --> 00:36:50,329
At that time,

629
00:36:50,840 --> 00:36:52,679
Sun Han Han would start to get anxious.

630
00:36:54,079 --> 00:36:55,639
Once she loses her temper,

631
00:36:56,079 --> 00:36:57,719
Zhou Bin will naturally get tired of her.

632
00:36:58,360 --> 00:36:59,719
What if she accepts it?

633
00:37:00,119 --> 00:37:01,519
How many years of youth do we have?

634
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,599
Sun Han Han has a high opinion of herself.

635
00:37:04,039 --> 00:37:05,199
Plus, she's not stupid.

636
00:37:05,559 --> 00:37:07,238
Why would she waste her golden years...

637
00:37:07,239 --> 00:37:08,329
being a third wheel?

638
00:37:09,769 --> 00:37:12,599
But would you still accept a man like that?

639
00:37:15,599 --> 00:37:16,599
Of course not.

640
00:37:17,480 --> 00:37:19,639
The divorce certificate is the worst card I have.

641
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:21,400
I'm going to turn it into a trump card.

642
00:37:22,039 --> 00:37:23,769
I just want to vent my frustration.

643
00:37:25,519 --> 00:37:28,440
I bet Zhou Bin will come back begging me to remarry him.

644
00:37:29,199 --> 00:37:31,480
At that time, I'll reject him and humiliate him.

645
00:37:32,000 --> 00:37:34,040
I also want Sun Han Han to see him for who he is...

646
00:37:34,559 --> 00:37:37,079
and ensure Zhou Bin loses everything.

647
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:44,880
How many more?

648
00:37:45,599 --> 00:37:46,639
Ten more.

649
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,720
- No. I can't do it anymore. - You can do it.

650
00:37:50,239 --> 00:37:51,840
- You can do it. - I can't.

651
00:37:52,519 --> 00:37:53,559
Hang in there.

652
00:37:56,079 --> 00:37:57,239
I really can't do it anymore.

653
00:37:57,559 --> 00:37:58,559
I can't do it.

654
00:38:00,639 --> 00:38:01,679
I can't do it.

655
00:38:01,880 --> 00:38:02,920
It's too tiring.

656
00:38:03,599 --> 00:38:05,559
I realize that women's periods of passion...

657
00:38:05,639 --> 00:38:06,880
last longer than men's.

658
00:38:07,519 --> 00:38:10,400
It's always men who come out of the honeymoon phase first.

659
00:38:12,289 --> 00:38:13,329
What do you mean?

660
00:38:15,000 --> 00:38:16,399
I'll always remember...

661
00:38:16,400 --> 00:38:17,880
how tireless...

662
00:38:18,039 --> 00:38:19,158
and youthful you looked,

663
00:38:19,159 --> 00:38:20,769
sweating it out in the gym.

664
00:38:22,039 --> 00:38:23,558
Now that we're together,

665
00:38:23,559 --> 00:38:25,199
you've lost that energy inside and out.

666
00:38:30,159 --> 00:38:31,239
I really can't do it today.

667
00:38:32,199 --> 00:38:33,239
Let's do it another day.

668
00:38:34,559 --> 00:38:36,329
You promised to persevere.

669
00:38:39,519 --> 00:38:40,840
I let you have your way too much.

670
00:38:41,000 --> 00:38:42,400
I knew it wasn't good,

671
00:38:42,480 --> 00:38:43,680
but I pretended not to see it.

672
00:38:44,289 --> 00:38:46,329
The busier you are, the more you have to persevere.

673
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,960
That's the only way I can be motivated every day.

674
00:38:50,360 --> 00:38:51,440
Mr. Zhou.

675
00:38:51,519 --> 00:38:52,559
Mr. Wang.

676
00:38:53,480 --> 00:38:54,519
It has been a while.

677
00:38:54,639 --> 00:38:55,920
Yes. It has been a while.

678
00:38:56,719 --> 00:38:57,809
This is Ya Ya.

679
00:38:57,920 --> 00:38:59,559
You've met before, right?

680
00:39:01,199 --> 00:39:02,199
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

681
00:39:02,809 --> 00:39:03,879
I kind of remember.

682
00:39:03,880 --> 00:39:04,920
Hello.

683
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,439
This is my niece.

684
00:39:06,440 --> 00:39:07,520
She just came to Jiangzhou.

685
00:39:08,599 --> 00:39:09,639
Hello.

686
00:39:10,679 --> 00:39:11,816
You just got here too, right?

687
00:39:11,840 --> 00:39:12,840
Yes.

688
00:39:12,841 --> 00:39:13,920
We'll go in first.

689
00:39:14,329 --> 00:39:15,399
Let's have a meal together next time.

690
00:39:15,400 --> 00:39:16,400
Sure.

691
00:39:20,329 --> 00:39:21,400
Han Han.

692
00:39:22,000 --> 00:39:23,079
What's wrong?

693
00:39:23,920 --> 00:39:25,000
Who's your niece?

694
00:39:28,000 --> 00:39:29,336
Back when we were at the hospital,

695
00:39:29,360 --> 00:39:31,289
who was it that followed me around every day...

696
00:39:31,329 --> 00:39:32,449
and kept calling me "uncle"?

697
00:39:34,000 --> 00:39:35,719
Is Mr. Wang also Zeng Cheng's friend?

698
00:39:39,880 --> 00:39:42,000
Look. I'm so tired today.

699
00:39:42,159 --> 00:39:43,919
Let's take a shower and find a place to eat.

700
00:40:09,519 --> 00:40:10,799
How long have you been together?

701
00:40:12,559 --> 00:40:13,559
What?

702
00:40:15,440 --> 00:40:17,135
When we bumped into familiar faces outside,

703
00:40:17,159 --> 00:40:18,559
he'd tell them that I'm his cousin.

704
00:40:20,519 --> 00:40:21,719
These people are so funny.

705
00:40:22,679 --> 00:40:24,000
Who doesn't know that?

706
00:40:24,239 --> 00:40:25,360
They're still pretending.

707
00:40:31,559 --> 00:40:32,599
I'm leaving.

708
00:41:17,360 --> 00:41:19,000
Didn't you two make it clear?

709
00:41:19,039 --> 00:41:20,519
Why are you still lying to me?

710
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:22,840
When will you tell me the truth?

711
00:41:23,480 --> 00:41:24,599
I'm going to remarry her.

712
00:41:26,000 --> 00:41:27,719
All my assets, stocks,

713
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:28,920
and cash...

714
00:41:28,960 --> 00:41:30,039
are under her name.

715
00:41:30,199 --> 00:41:31,558
This is the only way I can get back what's mine.

716
00:41:31,559 --> 00:41:32,759
Don't worry. I'll divorce her.

717
00:41:33,639 --> 00:41:34,639
You're single now,

718
00:41:34,679 --> 00:41:36,840
yet you can't be with me wholeheartedly.

719
00:41:37,239 --> 00:41:39,495
And you want to remarry and make me wait for your divorce?

720
00:41:39,519 --> 00:41:41,359
Then are you willing to bear the debt with me?

721
00:41:43,159 --> 00:41:44,159
I'll be honest with you.

722
00:41:44,440 --> 00:41:45,720
I don't have a penny to my name.

723
00:41:46,329 --> 00:41:48,400
All the expenses were paid in advance by the firm.

724
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:50,238
Zeng Cheng is the firm's major shareholder.

725
00:41:50,239 --> 00:41:52,479
If she turns against me and digs up the past one by one,

726
00:41:52,559 --> 00:41:54,199
my assets will immediately turn negative.

727
00:41:55,079 --> 00:41:56,400
Zhou Bin, you're too greedy.

728
00:41:57,559 --> 00:41:59,679
If you want to hear the truth, I can tell you now.

729
00:41:59,719 --> 00:42:01,615
That would mean suffering and living on nothing.

730
00:42:01,639 --> 00:42:02,679
Are you up for that?

731
00:42:04,719 --> 00:42:06,678
You don't have to threaten me with these words.

732
00:42:06,679 --> 00:42:07,960
I have my own job.

733
00:42:08,000 --> 00:42:09,840
I can live without you supporting me.

734
00:42:10,519 --> 00:42:11,840
Also, I have my limits.

735
00:42:12,329 --> 00:42:14,039
I can't be your mistress.

736
00:42:14,239 --> 00:42:15,328
Can you put away that whole independent woman act...

737
00:42:15,329 --> 00:42:16,329
for a moment?

738
00:42:16,360 --> 00:42:17,440
Look around you.

739
00:42:18,920 --> 00:42:20,159
I've worked so hard...

740
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:21,640
to give you the life you want.

741
00:42:22,329 --> 00:42:23,376
Depending solely on yourself,

742
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:25,360
it could take you 10 or 20 years to achieve that.

743
00:42:27,880 --> 00:42:29,785
If I were just a middle-aged man with nothing to show for myself...

744
00:42:29,809 --> 00:42:31,238
and no money,

745
00:42:31,239 --> 00:42:32,559
would you even spare me a glance?

746
00:42:33,559 --> 00:42:35,119
Who doesn't yearn for romance?

747
00:42:35,360 --> 00:42:36,680
Who doesn't yearn for sweet talk?

748
00:42:37,519 --> 00:42:38,599
But the reality...

749
00:42:38,960 --> 00:42:39,960
is too harsh.

750
00:42:42,239 --> 00:42:44,079
Every decision I'm making now...

751
00:42:44,559 --> 00:42:46,679
is for the future of both of us.

752
00:42:47,769 --> 00:42:48,840
That's the reality.

753
00:42:52,639 --> 00:42:53,679
Leave.

754
00:43:01,199 --> 00:43:02,199
Han Han.

755
00:43:04,159 --> 00:43:05,159
Romanticism...

756
00:43:07,440 --> 00:43:08,719
requires realism...

757
00:43:09,599 --> 00:43:10,678
and even utilitarianism...

758
00:43:10,679 --> 00:43:11,679
to sustain it.

759
00:43:14,079 --> 00:43:15,239
What we seek is love.

760
00:43:15,519 --> 00:43:16,769
We should relish love...

761
00:43:17,960 --> 00:43:19,160
instead of sacrificing for it.
